{"tid":1137673,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"被問會否斬許志安老母十碌　杜琪峯：打過電話問候Sammi","createTime":"2019-05-04T03:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T05:12:35.000Z","uid":20933,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2af2dfff9e05176a4ccf3dd99a029048178eef00","tid":1137673,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-dus1-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/b244ce08044e1ef4e6bc81e46a28ceca/5D3E2DC6/t51.2885-15/fr/e15/s1080x1080/55899996_2195321507228296_8466073762236931681_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-dus1-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;ig_cache_key=MjAyMzIxOTY4MTc4MDI1MTE0MA%3D%3D.2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-dus1-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2Fb244ce08044e1ef4e6bc81e46a28ceca%2F5D3E2DC6%2Ft51.2885-15%2Ffr%2Fe15%2Fs1080x1080%2F55899996_2195321507228296_8466073762236931681_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-dus1-1.cdninstagram.com%26ig_cache_key%3DMjAyMzIxOTY4MTc4MDI1MTE0MA%253D%253D.2&h=8507afa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上月被《蘋果》獨家踢爆許志安背着妻子鄭秀文（Sammi）與黃心穎偷食，由於著名導演杜琪峯（杜Sir）一向疼錫Sammi，直指Sammi是自己愛將，早在11年Sammi與安仔復合時，杜Sir曾警告安仔嚴禁飛甩Sammi，又揚言：「如果安仔揼咗佢，我斬佢老母十碌。」想必「安心偷食」令一向愛錫Sammi的杜Sir極為痛心。（相關新聞： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IBJHHt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IBJHHt&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW9yPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=66bebd76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IBJHHt</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n上月22日是杜Sir的64歲生日，過往他多數會與Sammi等大班好友食飯慶祝，但今次不但未見杜Sir舉行生日飯局，當日大批傳媒在杜Sir西貢寓所等候，亦不見他的蹤影。<br />\n<br />\n直至前晚，《蘋果》終見到杜Sir現身，大約在晚上8時許，見他駕車接載拍檔游乃海到九龍城一潮州菜館開餐，杜Sir與游乃海坐在近門口位置，兩人邊食邊傾偈，逗留了近2小時才擔住雪茄離開。杜Sir見到記者時面帶笑容，問他近期有沒有見過Sammi，他說：「冇。」有沒有打電話問候Sammi？杜Sir說：「當然有啦。」杜Sir曾揚言若安仔撇Sammi的話，會「斬佢老母十碌」，記者問會否找安仔算賬？杜Sir說：「唔好喺傷口度灑鹽。」說罷他便駕車離開。"},{"pid":"41dd00c3ecba900e040738113ef52aa226365714","tid":1137673,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:39:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190504/59558547\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190504%2F59558547&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW9yPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=10e6e88c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190504%2F59558547&h=96443283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190504/59558547</a>"},{"pid":"f27c44467f914847474d23628dc0e87d953d28d2","tid":1137673,"uid":94828,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:39:48.000Z","msg":"垃圾淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a1cf231d7243ccfdffcd750e4dc549251badc9","tid":1137673,"uid":188,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:41:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">如果安仔揼咗佢，我斬佢老母十碌</span><br />\n黑警又扮睇唔到? 恐嚇喎 做咩縮返入老母閪?"},{"pid":"8c1ad49bdd6eba05ea38a661cab9f924421ca6c5","tid":1137673,"uid":155682,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"杜sir ： 佢偷食啫，冇揼到Sammi，我出師無名。"},{"pid":"40bd4d3409079dad4269d3ae6d5f0f483aeda96c","tid":1137673,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />d黑社會不嬲都係口講咋麻"},{"pid":"054c65349d4413b731e471a18a935b71b584c577","tid":1137673,"uid":140218,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:46:38.000Z","msg":"杜Sir說：「唔好喺傷口度灑鹽。」說罷他便駕車離開。<br />\n<br />\n型"},{"pid":"a12352e15e03050b46e6425ebe1b03868c1ec2b5","tid":1137673,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:47:28.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"eb99ed1b350561b7ecacea837158b009862e1113","tid":1137673,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:47:42.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"16468e2c5c2